rious Gorge</h3>\n<table width=\"100%\" class=\"tborder\">\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Names</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">Curious Gorge <i><font size=\"-2\">",
    "</font></i></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Country</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?c=China\" title=\"Search for all threat groups from China\" class=\"inlink\"><img src=\"/img/flags/China.png\" alt=\"China\" width=\"33\" height=\"20\" /> China</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Sponsor</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">State-sponsored, PLA SSF</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Motivation</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?m=Information%20theft%20and%20espionage\" title=\"Search for all threat groups with motivation Information theft and espionage\" class=\"inlink\">Information theft and espionage</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">First seen</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">2022</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Description</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">",
    "A group TAG attributes to China's PLA SSF, has conducted campaigns against government and military organizations in Ukraine, Russia, Kazakhstan, and Mongolia. While this activity largely does not impact Google products, we remain engaged and are providing notifications to victim organizations.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Observed</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">Sectors: <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Defense\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Defense\" class=\"inlink\">Defense</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Government\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Government\" class=\"inlink\">Government</a>.<br />Countries: <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Kazakhstan\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Kazakhstan\" class=\"inlink\">Kazakhstan</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Mongolia\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Mongolia\" class=\"inlink\">Mongolia</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Russia\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Russia\" class=\"inlink\">Russia</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Ukraine\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Ukraine\" class=\"inlink\">Ukraine</a>.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Tools used</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" rowspan=\"1\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Operations performed</td><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\">Apr 2022</td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"100%\">Curious Gorge, a group TAG attributes to China's PLA SSF, has remained active against government, military, logistics and manufacturing organizations in Ukraine, Russia and Central Asia.<br />&lt;<a href=\"https://blog.google/threat-analysis-group/update-on-cyber-activity-in-eastern-europe/\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.google/threat-analysis-group/update-on-cyber-activity-in-eastern-europe/</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Information</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">&lt;<a href=\"https://blog.google/threat-analysis-group/tracking-cyber-activity-eastern-europe/\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.google/threat-analysis-group/tracking-cyber-activity-eastern-europe/</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p>Last change to this card: 04 May 2022</p>\n<p>Download this actor card in <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=Curious%20Gorge&o=p\" title=\"Download this card in PDF format\" class=\"inlink\">PDF</a> or <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=Curious%20Gorge&o=j\" title=\"Download this card in JSON format\" class=\"inlink\">JSON</a> format</p>\n<div class=\"backtotop\"><a href=\"#top\" title=\"Back to the top\" class=\"inlink\">&uarr;</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr><td width=\"80%\" rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\">\n<p>Infrastructure and Security Department<br />\nElectronic Transactions Development Agency</p>\n<h3>Follow us on</h3>\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/ETDA.Thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-facebook.png\" alt=\"Facebook\" title=\"Follow us on Facebook\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/etda_thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-twitter.png\" alt=\"Twitter\" title=\"Follow us on Twitter\" /></a>\n</td><td colspan=\"2\">\n<h3>Report incidents</h3>\n</td>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"0%\"><img src=\"/img/icon-phone.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" alt=\"Telephone\" title=\"Telephone\" /></td>\n<td width=\"20%\"><strong>+66"
